{"id":232955796,"title":"關於我的，小公舉","content":"當家人問起妳，\n我始終沒有更好的答案\n但妳依然是那樣的美好。\n\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/09ae84a0-2eb2-4c15-934a-85c1ac3397e8/1280.jpeg\n\n\n希望妳替我好好照顧自己\n希望妳替我好好疼愛自己\n希望妳替我好好保護自己\n希望妳別像個小笨蛋\n總是讓自己瘀青受傷\n別忘了妳依然是我的小公主\n怎麼能讓自己受傷了呢\n我說過妳受傷我會難過\n妳流眼淚我會心痛\n以前、現在，都是.\n希望妳不要不開心\n希望妳這樣快快樂樂\n\n我要妳保護好自己\n我要妳快快樂樂的\n不是希望了，是命令。\n\n如果妳沒有保護照顧好自己\n我真的怕我會忍不住.\n拜託妳 替我\n保護好、照顧好自己。\n\n我真的一樣愛妳啊，\n也很想妳\n是真的。\n\n🙃","excerpt":"當家人問起妳，我始終沒有更好的答案，但妳依然是那樣的美好。希望妳替我好好照顧自己，希望妳替我好好疼愛自己，希望妳替我好好保護自己，希望妳別像個小笨蛋，總是讓自己瘀青受傷，別忘了妳依然是我的小公主，怎麼","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"b5b2653a-6304-4564-9ea0-a4cec0be7aee","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-25T12:11:17.667Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-25T19:03:18.854Z","commentCount":1,"likeCount":19,"tags":[],"topics":["Les","彩虹","小公舉"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"彩虹","forumAlias":"rainbow","school":"棕熊小鯊魚","department":"kcwait1221","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":19}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/09ae84a0-2eb2-4c15-934a-85c1ac3397e8/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"567beb6c-46ab-4a7e-97a0-6eafcbd1a019","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/09ae84a0-2eb2-4c15-934a-85c1ac3397e8/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/09ae84a0-2eb2-4c15-934a-85c1ac3397e8/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/09ae84a0-2eb2-4c15-934a-85c1ac3397e8/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-25T12:11:17.667Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-25T19:03:18.854Z","width":360,"height":640},{"id":"567beb6c-46ab-4a7e-97a0-6eafcbd1a019","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/09ae84a0-2eb2-4c15-9